column5: Smokey and I are meeting there at 1:00 today....anybody else going ??
Hopefully you won't be bored silly and you'll still be there around 4:30 when I hope to get there. I'll look for your smiling face.
The wife and I will be there for 1:00pm  Doug

Wish I could but I buggered up my knee playing ball hockey last Saturday and don't think I'd be able to do all that walking. Enjoy the show and if you get a chance see if there is anyone there selling lure making supplies and molds for sinkers. I think I would like to get into doing some of that stuff and am just starting to try to get some contacts.  Hope you enjoy the show!
tinbanger and i will be there around 4:00
Sadly no, I have too much running around to do, but I am going Saturday.  Let us know how it is will you?  Maureen
I got an e-mail from Don and he and Ruth will be there this aft. as well. He was also thinking that Uncle Buck may be around.  See you this aft.

I won't be able to make it today guys.  Sorry you will miss me!!  If you find any hot deals post them on here, because I plan to skip work tomorrow to head on down.  Hopefully the boss dosen't see this  my 2 cents  2many
Bly and I will be going on Sunday....as long as my tickets from TJ arrive in the mail by tomorrow!!!
You and Mike have a good time, Lew. Sorry I can't join you.
Al;l the last tickets were mailed out the day befpore yesterday... so tuesaday,,, they should come in today or tomorrow...
Thanks TJ...looking forward to it!
I might try to get out there between 1-5

I was planning on going Saturday, but it turns out the boss called work off. Looks like I have some time to kill. My better half and self will be there today....leaving soon, I guess. I want to catch the Pike and Muskie seminars starting at 130 and will need time to fill a bag with stuff before that... C-U-There!

OK, I'll see you guys there, and sorry you can't make it Jim, but we'll get together next time.  REALLY lookin forward to Gord Pyzer's musky seminar at 2:15, I listened to his talk at the Odyssee 2 years ago and it was excellent !!....the man really knows his stuff !!  Thanks again TJ
Lew have a blast!!  try not to spend too much cash!
My wife and I will be there Saturday, parents are coming too!!  (they want to find a new fly-in lodge to go to this summer).  Entropy

Ill be there all day Saturday signing autographs.  If you don't have my headshot you can print it off of my profile page... here...  http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showuser=3  LOL....  have fun today dudes...
LOL TJ...I'll print a few hundred off and hand them out at the front door for you.....  BTW....bly called me from home...the tickets showed up today. Thanks again!

If anyone is going to the show tonight i was hoping to catch a ride. I live in ajax but i am in markham (close to 407 and kennedy.) till later tonight. anyone avail? will of course pitchin or pay for gas
Hey TJ,Mine havent arived yet either........................................Oh ya,I didnt win.LOL   Enjoy the show all.
Hey Lew,  Great pleasure to meet you and Smokey today.  Hope my memory lasts so I use some of the musky tips we saw.  See ya
